divs: Sighting DetailsWas attending dinner party approx time of event 9 and 10 pm eastern time over looking the entrance to tampa bay egmont key light was visible to the left approx 45 degrees to the left of the observed object attempting to call attention to other person present to no avail object gave off steady reddish yellow light low elevation beyond edmont key greater than 5 miles traveled approx due north at extreme speed changed direction approx 90 degrees into a vertical climb and then disappeared entire event approx lasted less than 10 seconds would like to know if any other individuals witnessed this event ?
Summary: Looked very similar to a Standard Missile launch except for flight trajectory
